---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Judo at the [2015 Pan American Games](/2015_Pan_American_Games) in [Toronto](/Toronto) was a four-day exhibition of disciplined aggression and calculated strategy. These martial arts contests, part of the larger Pan American sporting spectacle, were held from July 11 to 14, 2015. The designated battleground was the [Hershey Centre](/Paramount_Fine_Foods_Centre) in [Mississauga](/Mississauga), a city within the Greater [Toronto](/Toronto) Area. However, due to the ever-present influence of corporate sponsorship and naming rights, the venue was officially referred to as the "Mississauga Sports Centre" for the duration of the games. A minor detail, perhaps, but one that highlights the transactional nature of modern athletics.

The competition comprised a total of fourteen distinct [judo](/Judo) events, meticulously divided into seven categories for men and an equal seven for women. This balanced allocation ensured that both genders had ample opportunity to demonstrate their mastery of the art. The rigorous qualification process ultimately brought together 135 competitors from 19 different nations across the Americas, each vying for the coveted medals. For those with a penchant for historical context, these games followed the [judo](/Judo) events at the [2011 Pan American Games](/Judo_at_the_2011_Pan_American_Games) and preceded those at the [2019 Pan American Games](/Judo_at_the_2019_Pan_American_Games), forming a continuous thread in the tapestry of continental sports. Further statistical insights and detailed results can, of course, be found through the external databases of the [International Judo Federation](/International_Judo_Federation) (IJF) and JudoInside.com, if one is so inclined to pore over such things.

